UID:b506a2b1-32fb-50cf-b08e-67089bb0fba5
SUMMARY:Community Consultation - VPN Restrictions
DESCRIPTION:This draft policy brief explores the growing efforts by some governments
  to ban\, restrict\, or control the use of Virtual Private Networks (VPN
 s)\, and provides principles and recommendations for addressing related 
 policy concerns.
